{
  "stem": "23730.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the start of our Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the start.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from Dunajska Streda, the family eventually-- Before we go further--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was by the Slovak fascists, it was orchestrated, under the influence of the German neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- it was revenge, because you must remember, at the time, Slovakia had to hand over to Hungary, the-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know in English-- the [NON-ENGLISH]-- the-- you know-- the overland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like-- like-- territories they had to hand back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was promised by the Fuhrer, Horty got the promise, you will get these territories-- and the Slovaks were bitter about it, very bitter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the first revenge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And who suffers first?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a promise to seed some of the uplands of Slovakia to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Highlands",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were so bitter about it, the Slovaks, and we had to suffer first.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were the first that they call today ethnic cleansing, but in a very, very harsh way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not yet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was only the Jewish population if of Hungarian background.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were many, many, but it didn't apply yet to the whole population of Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, several hundreds, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The community there was absolutely fantastic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On Shabbat, everybody had where to sleep on that night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember even, on Shabbat's morning, we had already a wonderful Kiddush there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The doors were open to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did whatever humanly possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But how long can you stay?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed one week there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed with a family, Vice, who were just wonderful-- too wonderful for words how they treated us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were already refugees, remember-- refugees!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually the family-- I went to Papa, to grandfather [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] alone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Papa being the city in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
